metadata.description: This Emoji Base is a genesis token for RMX Party and the first incarnation Cursed Emoji designed by artist yung jake. It will serve as a RMX Pass and give you access to the RMX Console for you to remix a second incarnation Cursed Emoji. Remixed Emoji Bases will unlock access to new drops and other features at rmx.party.
metadata.name: RMX Pass: Emoji Base
